23 (i) through a clear link or tab; and
24 (ii) in a searchable format.
25 (3) The provider directory shall include:
26 (i) for each provider on the carrier’s provider panel:
27 1. the name of the provider;
28 2. the specialty areas of the provider;
29 3. whether the provider currently is accepting new patients;

