17 (ii) billing for health care services provided to enrollees of the carrier
18 using a different federal tax identification number than that used by the group practice or
19 health care facility under a contract with the carrier.
20 (2) A nonparticipating provider shall notify an enrollee:
21 (i) that the provider does not participate on the provider panel of
22 the enrollee’s carrier; and
23 (ii) of the anticipated total charges for the health care services.
